{"tid":379114,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那賤婦襲國泰空姐   試圖違返保釋條件離港  裁判官准續保","createTime":"2017-08-29T04:38:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-29T04:58:21.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b503b7c79bf8ac507cc3747d85053d1274bd67e4","tid":379114,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T04:38:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170829/large/29ls3p02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170829%2Flarge%2F29ls3p02.jpg&h=bb25d37b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】支那女乘客上月乘坐國泰航機由曼谷回港，其間涉嫌推撞一名空姐及踢傷對方左腳，被控普通襲擊罪。案件昨在西九龍法院再提堂，辯方申請押後答辯，待與律政司商討以其他方式處理案件。裁判官批准押後至9月25日再訊，准她繼續保釋。<br />\n<br />\n申改保釋條件被拒<br />\n<br />\n女乘客早前獲准保釋但不可離港，惟她曾試圖離港，在關口遭截獲押上法庭後解釋是想回大陸探望病父，她昨申請更改保釋條件但被拒。<br />\n<br />\n被告劉曉曉（34歲）報稱從事廣告業，控罪指她於上月14日在航機上襲擊女子阮亦雯（29歲）。據了解，劉因收拾餐盤問題而與阮發生爭執，繼而有肢體碰撞。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：WKCC3496/17"},{"pid":"3dc4e79bbf3a265d56094745b6ceed4cbf357735","tid":379114,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T04:56:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ff3c95c42bb5be130e351cda95790eadd468cd1","tid":379114,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T04:57:40.000Z","msg":"好恐怖"},{"pid":"ecb247d54b5207c531fbb56d50eeb40d29f97012","tid":379114,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T04:58:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}